'''2011年加拿大聯邦大選舞弊醜聞'''是[[2011年加拿大聯邦大選|2011年加拿大聯邦大選]]期間發生的政治醜聞。在事件中[[加拿大保守黨|保守黨]]競選辦公室涉嫌以電話向選民發放虛假信息，告知選民投票站地址有所改動，企圖透過抑制投票率從而干擾選舉結果。加拿大選舉管理局共接獲247宗相關投訴，涉及308個選區。<ref name="CanadianPressAug21">{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2012/08/21/court-records-say-robocall-complaints-doubled-to-1394-specific-occurrences-in-last-years-election/|title=Court records say robocall complaints doubled to 1,394 'specific occurrences' in last year’s election|publisher=National Post|date=2012-08-21|access-date=2016-10-09|archive-date=2021-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210807203942/https://nationalpost.com/category/news/}}</ref>由於根據加拿大選舉法，故意阻礙任何選民在選舉中投票是非法行為，[[加拿大皇家騎警|加拿大皇家騎警]]（RCMP）及選舉管理局為此展開調查。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/acts/E-2.01/section-281.html |title=Canada Elections Act 281(g) |publisher=Department of Justice Canada |accessdate=2016-10-10 |archive-date=2016-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161012224609/http://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/acts/E-2.01/section-281.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/acts/E-2.01/section-491.html |title=Canada Elections Act 491(3)(d) |publisher=Department of Justice Canada |accessdate=2016-10-10 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111234629/https://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/acts/E-2.01/section-491.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>事件迅速受到全國媒體的關注，導致2012年3月至4月期間至少27個城市的一連串抗議行動。<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.baytoday.ca/content/news/details.asp?c=46217|title = Thousands to rally against 'Robocall' election fraud|date = 2012-03-15|work = Bay Today|accessdate = 2016-10-09|archive-date = 2014-04-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140424225706/http://www.baytoday.ca/content/news/details.asp?c=46217|dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 事件 ==
在2011年加拿大聯邦大選期間，包括[[安大略省|安大略省]][[貴湖|貴湖]]在內的至少14個選區的選民收到有關選舉的誤導性電話。<ref>{{cite news|title=Robocall controversy hasn't hurt support for Tories: poll|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2012/03/11/robocall-controversy-hasnt-hurt-support-for-tories-poll/|newspaper=National Post|date=2012-03-21|accessdate=2016-10-09|archive-date=2021-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210807204008/https://nationalpost.com/category/news/}}</ref>該欺詐電話在選舉日的前一天透過電話系統公司RackNine致電選民，指示他們往錯誤的投票站投票。內容中有人冒充選舉管理局職員：「這是來自加拿大選舉管理局的自動系統訊息，由於選民投票率預計會增加，您的投票地點已更改。新的投票地點在[[雲咸街|雲咸街]]北55號老魁北克街購物中心。重複，新的投票地點在雲咸街北55號老魁北克街購物中心，如果您有任何疑問，請撥打[[熱線|熱線]]1-800-443-4456，我們對可能造成的任何不便表示歉意。」<ref name="nationalpost3">{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2012/02/23/stephen-harper-denies-tories-knew-about-illegal-election-robocalls-linked-to-party/?__lsa=7ccc758d |title=Racknine 'Robocalls' are the fault of Stephen Harper's 'Nixonian culture'|publisher=National Post|date=2012-02-23}}</ref>

選舉日當天上午10:00後，欺詐電話在短時間內致電了數以千計的[[貴湖|貴湖]]選民。由於選舉管理局收到大量投訴，地區選舉主任隨即打電話到電台，呼籲市民無需理會該欺詐電話。<ref name="PostMediaMar12">{{cite news|url = http://news.nationalpost.com/2012/03/12/liberals-say-abortion-robocall-not-voter-suppression/|title = Abortion robocall attacking Tories in Guelph was not voter suppression: Liberals|date = 2012-03-12|work = National Post|accessdate = 2016-10-12|archive-date = 2021-08-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210807204008/https://nationalpost.com/category/news/}}</ref>但在一個小時內，仍有150到200名選民趕到假的投票地點，有選民得知受騙後憤而撕掉了自己的選民證。<ref name="MaherFeb23">{{cite news|url = http://www.vancouversun.com/news/Robocalls+tried+discourage+voters/6196549/story.html|title = 'Robocalls' tried to discourage voters|date = 2012-02-23|work = Vancouver Sun}}{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>上午11:06，選舉局專員安妮塔發送了一封緊急[[電子郵件|電子郵件]]給法律顧問，報告選舉主任亦致電詢問欺詐電話的事。基於[[陽光法案|陽光法案]]的規定，當時政府部門的內部文件在其後公開予公眾查閱。一封公開的電子郵件顯示，法律顧問致函給選舉事務副主任羅尼莫爾納，稱今次事件已不能以「嚴重」來形容，因主事者已擾亂了整個選舉的投票過程。<ref name="NoilesMar07">{{cite news|url = http://www.viewmag.com/14108-Robocalls+Target+Liberals.htm|title = Robocalls Target Liberals|date = 2012-03-07|work = View Magazine|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140429234843/http://www.viewmag.com/14108-Robocalls+Target+Liberals.htm|archivedate = 2014-04-29|accessdate = 2016-10-12}}</ref>

選舉管理局追查到欺詐電話來自[[魁北克省|魁北克省]]西南部一個城市，並傳訊了該手機供應商。手機供應商提供的資料顯示，貴湖區[[加拿大保守黨|保守黨]]候選人馬蒂·伯克（Marty Burke）及貴湖區保守黨辦公室曾在大選前與電話系統公司RackNine有過31通電話。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.winnipegfreepress.com/breakingnews/harper-says-tories-not-behind-robocalls-accuses-opposition-of-smear-campaign-140937823.html |title=Harper says Tories not behind robocalls; accuses opposition of smear campaign |publisher=Winnipeg Free Press |date=2012-02-29 |accessdate=2016-10-12 |archive-date=2012-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120301005308/http://www.winnipegfreepress.com/breakingnews/harper-says-tories-not-behind-robocalls-accuses-opposition-of-smear-campaign-140937823.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>儘管如此，這並未足以證明保守黨是這次事件中的幕後主腦。調查在此後開始進入[[瓶頸|瓶頸]]，雖然選舉管理局曾透過信用咭繳費資料及[[IP地址|IP地址]]追查涉事人物，但最後都徒勞無功。由於進展不理想，[[加拿大皇家騎警|加拿大皇家騎警]]加入這場舞弊醜聞的調查團隊。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ottawacitizen.com/life/Trail+Pierre+Poutine+runs+into+open+WiFi+connection/7073441/story.html |title=Trail of Pierre Poutine runs into an open Wi-Fi connection |publisher=Ottawa Citizen |date=2012-05-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120812062320/http://www.ottawacitizen.com/life/Trail+Pierre+Poutine+runs+into+open+WiFi+connection/7073441/story.html |archivedate=2012-08-12 |accessdate=2016-10-12 }}</ref>

== 調查 ==
2012年5月4日，選舉局調查員向法庭提交的文件中指出，當天保守黨競選工作人員安德烈曾使用RackNine，而在4分鐘內本案中的選舉欺詐電話使用與安德烈相同的IP地址致電選民，而此IP地址當時屬於貴湖保守黨競選總部內的一台電腦。<ref name="McGregor04May12">{{cite news|url = http://www.ottawacitizen.com/life/Robocalls+address+same+used+Conservative+candidate+campaign+worker+Elections+Canada+alleges/6567696/story.html|title = Robocalls IP address same as one used by Conservative candidate campaign worker, Elections Canada alleges|date = 2012-05-04|work = Ottawa Citizen|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120508195928/http://www.ottawacitizen.com/life/Robocalls+address+same+used+Conservative+candidate+campaign+worker+Elections+Canada+alleges/6567696/story.html|archivedate = 2012-05-08|accessdate = 2016-10-12}}</ref>另外，安德烈又在4月30日從保守黨的[[數據庫|中央數據庫]]中下載了一份電話號碼列表，而欺詐電話的RackNine帳戶在同一天被創建。法庭傳召的證人指控，保守黨競選工作人員米高（Michael Sona）曾提出一個誤導性宣傳計劃，包括向非保守黨選民發送錯誤的票站地點。安德烈及米高於答辯中一再否認有參與事件。<ref name="Payton04May12">{{cite news|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2012/05/04/pol-robocalls-ip-address-traced.html|title = Robocalls linked to Guelph Tory campaign worker's computer|date = 2012-05-04|work = Canadian Broadcasting Corporation|accessdate = 2016-10-12|archive-date = 2013-09-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130910164134/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2012/05/04/pol-robocalls-ip-address-traced.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>

8月份，法庭續審時收到調查員更有力的證據，顯示安德烈與打出欺詐電話的人在2011年5月1日至2日深夜使用同一部電腦，兩者使用期間並沒有登出。科技專家解釋此法庭文件時表示，安德烈在5月1日至2日三度登入Racknine網路界面，最後一次登出後，欺詐電話的Racknine帳戶隨即被人重新登入，而兩者使用的是同一瀏覽器。另外，安德烈原使用[[網絡代理|網絡代理]]（Proxy）登入，但1分鐘後再次登錄時卻忘了使用網絡代理，無意中直接瀏覽網站，暴露了自己的IP地址來自保守黨競選辦公室（99.225.28.34）。 <ref name="OMalley28Aug12">{{cite news|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/inside-politics-blog/2012/08/newly-released-court-files-could-shed-new-light-on-the-mysterious-pierre-poutine.html|title = Court files could shed new light on the mysterious Pierre Poutine|date = 2012-08-29|work = Canadian Broadcasting Corporation|accessdate = 2016-10-12|archive-date = 2013-07-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130725070312/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/inside-politics-blog/2012/08/newly-released-court-files-could-shed-new-light-on-the-mysterious-pierre-poutine.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 定罪結果 ==
2014年8月，保守黨競選工作人員米高遭控違反《選舉法》，“畜意阻撓選民在選舉中投票”，處以9個月監禁及1年[[緩刑|緩刑]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kitchener.ctvnews.ca/guelph-campaign-worker-charged-in-fraudulent-robocall-affair-1.1221286|title=Guelph campaign worker charged in fraudulent robocall affair|publisher=CTV Kitchener News|date=2013-04-02|accessdate=2016-10-12|archive-date=2019-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414044141/https://kitchener.ctvnews.ca/guelph-campaign-worker-charged-in-fraudulent-robocall-affair-1.1221286|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖然初審法官曾言，米高不可能單獨執行此犯罪行為，但米高是事件中唯一一名受到檢控的保守黨人。

